  "text": "HCN production of the isolates was detected by the method of Bakker and Schippers [CITATION_1] . Briefly, HCN production was determined by the color change of the filter paper previously dipped in 2% sodium carbonate/0.05% picric acid solution and placed on the bacterial lawn. Brown color indicated the presence of HCN.",
